{"tid":1544641,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林奠聽日尖沙咀酒宴","createTime":"2019-09-05T15:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:04:56.000Z","uid":295101,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5ebce57266d602c9bc4943e3a916674ee53a2f58","tid":1544641,"uid":295101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:33:53.000Z","msg":"交際柒婆聽日尖沙咀出席酒宴(好似新K11)見中聯辦，商界!!<br />\n希望順利，冇麻包袋垃圾筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34624aea94b98fe01e5bbe93959a8d468b9aead","tid":1544641,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"又直升機？"},{"pid":"edb9bb0225601dc2c73f5c304506b9ab70139c13","tid":1544641,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e0278b42444c452d4cc12ad9b524a3823350e3f","tid":1544641,"uid":295101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"93e0145410ee6acea6b9440058299c4da8b1fa3e","tid":1544641,"uid":295101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0298e6f6b8bc3fa8a9fdc880871316b26f218d09","tid":1544641,"uid":295101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"33bf554a47ae2984e492d31df14199ca39239992","tid":1544641,"uid":34780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n太子CCTV最快星期6會被刪除<br />\n我地要有一次大集氣出太子 制造輿論壓力<br />\n將831死人嘅概念植入市民心中<br />\n令全港市民聚焦落黨鐵 迫佢交831嘅CCTV<br />\n絕對唔係要依兩日咁得幾十人圍太子警署咁<br />\n一定要上千人<br />\n實行將太子站鋪滿白色鮮花<br />\n<br />\n若然屬實 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日就係手足頭七</span></span><br />\n依家號召各位巴打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花</span></span><br />\n見字嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">巴打幫手spread出去</span></span> 一個人真係推唔起<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【831】9月6號1930集氣千人太子站獻花行動post<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544326</a>"},{"pid":"54842fc3d6e2bf67c3381350046d7daee188f563","tid":1544641,"uid":295101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:37:04.000Z","msg":"721.831"},{"pid":"04895d4f0b2879c459d01cd442fa06526b0a3b0b","tid":1544641,"uid":132362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"[究極賤格] 國織人道救援組織念力救港秘技大公開：「為香港祈禱」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dPtRCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dPtRCS</a>"},{"pid":"6824f4d61959af58c3efb52addf4db0a9e6121ba","tid":1544641,"uid":295101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:37:41.000Z","msg":"721.831"},{"pid":"cc74451a0f0e7b2613fab21ce5c6b29e36b65a1b","tid":1544641,"uid":92328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" cl